# GTH Gaussian basis sets for the GTH-PADE pseudopotentials.
# Transcribed from CP2K basis data.
# File format:
#   <Element> <BasisName> [aliases...]
#   <l> <nexp>              # one shell: angular momentum l, primitive count nexp
#     <exp> <coeff>         # nexp primitive lines (shared exps are repeated per shell)
#     ...
#   <l> <nexp>              # next shell ...
#
# Comments (`#`) and blank lines are ignored. Angular momenta: s=0, p=1, d=2, f=3.

